Carnival Eats - Season 2, Episode 3




From Derby Day to Down State

Host Noah Cappe is off to the races in Louisville Kentucky at the Kentucky Derby Festival where he chows down on a custom made pizza known as the Kentucky Hot Brown. Next he heads to Beaumont Texas for the South Texas State Fair where local specialties are The Swamp Thing and Hush Kitties.




Original Air Date: 30-Jul-2015
